    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing the absolute pinnacle of its model. The exterior paint retains its original showroom shine without a single blemish, and the interior is immaculate, showing no signs of wear whatsoever. Mechanically, the car performs flawlessly, having been meticulously maintained and garage-kept its entire life. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
