    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with perfection. The exterior shows some age with various small dings, minor scratches, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it may require some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in top shape. It's a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the high price tag of a pristine model.",
