    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in great shape for its next owner! It's super clean, runs smoothly, and honestly, it\u2019s just a blast to drive. I've taken great care of it, and it's got plenty of life left to give. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it feels on the road!",
