    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its six individual throttle bodies and is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The drivetrain is anchored by a functional M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal power delivery across the rear axle. Recent service highlights include a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a thorough subframe reinforcement inspection to ensure long-term structural rigidity. Riding on staggered Style 67 alloys, the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the communicative turn-in and high-speed stability characteristic of this chassis. A well-maintained performance icon that balances mechanical purity with daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, having been regularly detailed and garage-kept. While there are a few minor stone chips consistent with careful road use, the body remains straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, non-smoker environment. The premium upholstery is supple with only light natural creasing, and all onboard technology\u2014from the infotainment system to the climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a complete folder of service records included to prove its history. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts crisply, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. Recent updates include a fresh oil service and a cooling system flush. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without the need for any upcoming repairs.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
